{"tid":2311573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頂佢老母！民主黨嘅野 同共產黨一模一樣，係到掛羊頭賣狗肉","createTime":"2020-12-04T07:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T13:27:26.000Z","uid":7736,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d5e36110cd3a8b53fcdfdb28ae6978b8bfe3307","tid":2311573,"uid":7736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:19:03.000Z","msg":"A Michigan Democrat made the mistake of asking a witness just now why more witnesses don't come forward.  <br />\n<br />\nHer answer should go Viral:<br />\n<br />\n#MichiganHearing<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/majorpatriot/status/1334303711208894464?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmajorpatriot%2Fstatus%2F1334303711208894464%3Fs%3D21&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=a5937c9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmajorpatriot%2Fstatus%2F1334303711208894464%3Fs%3D21&h=3a46a370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/majorpatriot/status/1334303711208894464?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n這位名叫梅利莎&middot;卡隆（Melissa Carone）的女證人在作證時，受到了民主黨議員們的攻擊性質問。但她回應說：「我在宣誓書上簽名&hellip;&hellip;你簽過嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n當她作完證即將離開時，一名民主黨人突然問她：可以再問你一個簡單的問題嗎？為什麼除了你，並沒有其他更多的人站出來作證？<br />\n<br />\n梅利莎有些激動地回答說：「我來告訴你原因。 我的生活被摧毀了。我失去家人、朋友，我和我孩子被威脅。我需要搬家，換電話號碼，我甚至無法找到工作。因為威脅，沒人願意出來作證。民主黨就是要毀了你的生活。」然後，她一邊起身準備離開，一邊補充說：「就像他們對川普所做的一樣！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/12/03/a103001591.html?fbclid=IwAR3vEgclKtVAL-mQVHVz3qEbi82aFGrhpXwxs8IwitS1r1OC6ZhIx--Riss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F12%2F03%2Fa103001591.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3vEgclKtVAL-mQVHVz3qEbi82aFGrhpXwxs8IwitS1r1OC6ZhIx--Riss&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=fd67b086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/12/03/a103001591.html?fbclid=IwAR3vEgclKtVAL-mQVHVz3qEbi82aFGrhpXwxs8IwitS1r1OC6ZhIx--Riss</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋如果你係共和黨嘅人，會好難係政府搵到工！<br />\n如果你係共和黨嘅人，政府啲民主黨人 會搵機會炒你！<br />\n<br />\n龔小夏博士講過好多次<br />\n聽廣傳媒/袁弓夷個台會知更多<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2n8T29luG5Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2n8T29luG5Q&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGDk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=138790de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2n8T29luG5Q</a><br />\n33:70"},{"pid":"e0d3af7dd471c2f7eb5d1ac58de2ad58e834f273","tid":2311573,"uid":371606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}